{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_kaitou_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_kaitou_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"被折射的星光","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"过去的一年半，宝石匠海因茨经手的生意里，所有主顾都遭遇了不幸。而这次，他只有七天的时间，仿造一颗进献给双子女皇的珍稀晶石。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_kaitou_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["海因茨","伯爵侍从","伯爵打手","萨克森伯爵","？？？","米夏埃尔"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"1098年","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"莱塔尼亚恩瓦德大区，格林登","id":10},{"type":"dialog","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":13},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"唉......","id":15,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"眼睛总算没那么痛了，现在我终于能够入睡......","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":18},{"type":"charslot","id":19},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_doorbreak","id":20},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":21},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":22},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":23},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"搜仔细点！尤其是他桌上的设备！","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"别磨蹭，上锁的箱子直接炸开！书架都给我掀了！留声机也拆开看看！哼，附庸风雅的东西。","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"还有，你——","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"charslot","id":30},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":34},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"1","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"老实点，快说吧。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......抱歉，尊敬的老爷，您想让我说什么？我只知道，刚刚毁掉的那箱货物是顾客委托我转手的，价格不菲......","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"你在指责萨克森伯爵造成了你的损失？","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"不敢。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"顶着这么一双机灵的眼睛可不适合装傻，小子。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......所以，有什么任务，需要伯爵大人亲自走下高塔，跑来这间蜷缩在阴影之中的陋居？","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我很乐意效劳。","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"charslot","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵打手","text":"报告，我这边没有找到可疑的陷阱。","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵打手","text":"我这边也没有。","id":55},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"哼......算你有眼力。","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"所有人，退出去。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":59},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","channel":"1","id":60},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":62},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"1","id":63},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":65},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"真是遗憾，海因茨，我们不得不在这一片狼藉中会面，希望你不要介意。","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":71},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"50,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"当然不介意，伯爵大人。现在这间屋子已经谢绝会客了，请说吧。","id":74},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"......你很聪明，海因茨，这很好。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"charslot","id":80},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":81},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/23/Avg_bg_44_g6_towerterrace.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":82},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":83},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":85},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"大、大人......","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"伊维格娜德希望得到一颗独一无二的晶石作为今年女皇庆典的献礼，这项诏令颁布以来，有多少人跑断了腿。","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"我已经向女皇陛下承诺，格林登将满足她的心愿。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"我费了多少心思，才搜罗到那么一块双色晶石！","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"浓郁的黑色与透亮的金色交相辉映，没有哪种颜色多出一分一毫，也没有哪种颜色含有哪怕一丝杂质。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"完美的比例、完美的色泽，就像莱塔尼亚的“永恒恩典”与“无情权威”......","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"我称它为“双塔之梦”，没有比它更适合两位陛下的礼物！","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"女皇之声七天后便会到达格林登取走宝石。而在这个时候，居然有人在你们的重重守卫下窃走了它？","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"请问那窃贼的源石技艺是隔空取物，还是将自己变成空气？","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"或者说，一直以来，我都在养着一群废物？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"属下马上去追查，就算把整座移动城市都翻一遍......","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你们连对方是谁，用了怎样的手段都没有头绪。追查？","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"......去一趟海因茨那儿。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":107},{"type":"charslot","id":108},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":110},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":111},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":113},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"所以，您是希望我能......","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"不是希望，是命令。","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你为“双塔之梦”做过鉴定，你必定记得它梦幻的色泽、独特的星光——每一个人，只要见过它，就绝不可能忘记。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"把它重新造出来，海因茨，复现它璀璨夺目的样子！","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"可、可我只是宝石鉴定方面的一介学徒。这些切割设备只能用来满足自己的研究，最多给老爷们的乐器和法杖安装装饰性宝石。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"要让我僭越大师工匠的职责，凭空仿造那样一颗珍宝，实在有些强人所难。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"更何况，常见的仿造手段，恐怕很难瞒过女皇殿前的宝石学家。一旦此事暴露，我......","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"够了。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"我资助你，原本就是器重你在宝石鉴定、精密切割和晶石改造方面的天分。","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"听好，如果这一行跟音乐一样，有“首席”的说法，现在，至少在格林登，你离这个头衔不远了。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......如果能够从您那里获得这份殊荣，我将不胜感激。","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"当然，你更不要忘记，自己作为宝石鉴定师的知名度从何而来。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"别把自己也骗过去了。你不是第一次造假。我不介意失去一个帮手，可你未必能承担得起损失。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我没忘记。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我不会忘记，伯爵大人。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":138},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":139},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"charslot","id":141},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":142},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_bg_28_g2_slumstreets.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":143},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":144,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"唔......","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"——抱歉，请原谅我的冒昧。刚刚天气由阴转晴，您身上的亮色纽扣，光线变化很明显。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":150},{"type":"charslot","id":151},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":153},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"在如此昏暗曲折的小巷，也能利用光线折射探查周围的环境......呵，你是否有些过于戒备了？","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我不敢对伯爵的贴身护卫有任何意见。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"可我随身带着一批可能用于宝石仿造的材料，行走在这高塔庇护不到的平民区，不得不多一份谨慎。","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"当然......想到自己要欺瞒的对象，也难免心虚。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"既然您正好在，能否拜托您看看这些材料，是否与“双塔之梦”的材质接近？","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"唔......","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"不得不说，你的确值得伯爵的器重。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"抓住这次机遇吧，小子。一旦事成，伯爵博得了双子女皇的欢心，你会跟着沾光的。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"机遇......","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"多谢，只是这机遇实在令我惶恐。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我只是个痴情于宝石的普通人，本来......完全不懂什么加工伪造。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"但你应该很清楚，伯爵赏识的是你的哪一部分事迹。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......在我看来，那只是一系列阴差阳错。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我还记得自己第一次仿造的宝石，可以说，即使作为赝品，它也拙劣无比。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我既没有胆量选用足够好的原料，也缺乏用铅玻璃与树脂修补裂痕的手艺。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"只是作为那家珠宝行的小学徒，我能够在某些人的默许甚至授意下，绕过鉴定环节，将它放进展台。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"那段时间，我恐怕比现在还要心神不宁，时时刻刻准备抓起行囊逃跑，每个睡不着的夜晚都在犹豫要不要向治安队自首。","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"但你没有被揭穿。否则，我们现在不会在这里谈话。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......那枚假宝石很快被一位男爵斥巨资买走了，我也离开了那家珠宝行。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"后来我听说，他手头并不阔绰，原本是想赌那枚宝石能让他重新获得一名贵族应有的身家。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"结果我那拙劣的仿制品立刻被懂行的人识破，于是那位男爵发了疯，从此杳无音讯。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我想只是我运气很好，他这样一名贵族，下落竟然无人在意，因此我免于被追杀。","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"哈哈哈！只是一个男爵而已，这些抱着老爷们的鞋底沾得一点光的小贵族，当然无人在意。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"据我所知，你还为一名学者愚弄了他的对手，不是吗？","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"啊......那件事我就更无奈了。应该说，我只是犯下了一个错误。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"如您所知，我的法杖需要宝石碎晶驱动，这代价不算昂贵，因为那些切割下来的边角料本来就是废弃物。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"但不知为何，每个月固定送来碎晶的箱子里，那一次却赫然躺着一颗完整的宝石。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"你当真不知道为什么？","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我怎么敢细想呢？","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"在舞台上演出大变活人的魔术师，知道自己的机关失灵、铡刀真的会将志愿者切成两段的时候，恐怕也只能闭着眼睛下手吧？","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"后来我得知，一名书记官因为偷偷卖掉了自己看管的宝石又无法找回，受到了严厉的惩罚。","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"可那时......宝石的确已经成了我试管中的晶末。","id":206,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"还有......","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"还有使伯爵留意到你的那份假鉴定书。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我原本以为萨克森伯爵派人找上门来，是要让我为他的侄子，一位尊贵子爵所丧失的名誉付出代价。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"你只是按照要求，写了一份完美的鉴定书，将次级宝石鉴定成了世间少有的珍宝。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"错在萨克森子爵自己竟不知天高地厚，将假鉴定书与宝石放在一起四处展示，招人笑话。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"是啊，我只是......按照要求。","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"伯爵大人不仅没有动怒，反而理解并愿意器重我。直至今日，我都不知该如何表达自己对这份错爱的感激。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"只要你忠心地按照我们的吩咐做事就够了。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"你的惶恐也是伯爵器重你的原因之一，海因茨。你不需要太狡猾。","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"是。","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"好了，闲聊时间结束。","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"女皇之声还有三天就会到达格林登，如果我们拿出的献礼有任何瑕疵，恐怕伯爵的高塔都将变为平地。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"你该回到你的工作台前了。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_498_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":228},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":229},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":230},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"将我推到今天这一步的，还有一个与宝石相关的故事。","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"一个矿场无端在爆炸中塌陷的故事。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"只是，一名贵族的死活都无人在意，这个有关可怜普通人的故事......当然也不值得他人过问，对吧？","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":239},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":240},{"type":"charslot","id":241},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":242},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/23/Avg_bg_44_g6_towerterrace.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":245},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","duration":"1.5","id":246},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"（口哨）♪","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"（口哨）♪♪","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":250},{"type":"charslot","id":251},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":252},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"别再让我听到这样粗鄙的口哨声，海因茨。至少在我的高塔上，这是禁止的。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"抱歉。只是情不自禁，伯爵大人。","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我头一回站在这么高的地方，一位伯爵的高塔之上。从这里往下看，格林登的所有建筑，都像是佝偻着腰，怎么都直不起来。","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"......","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"海因茨，我不是来听你抒发人生感悟的。女皇之声今天就会到......“双塔之梦”呢？","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"已经放在了桌上，伯爵大人。","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":264},{"type":"charslot","id":265},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_open_box","id":266},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":267},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"小时候，我站在脏兮兮的棚屋前面，总喜欢拧着脖子抬头看。","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"那时候老是没来由地瞎想，什么时候能到高塔的顶上吹吹风。高处的风，一定很干净......","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":271},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"海因茨，闭嘴！","id":273,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"这就是你为我仿造的宝石？这就是“双塔之梦”？","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"charslot","id":276},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":277,"musicid":2},{"type":"text","text":"装着宝石的木匣被扔到了地上，伯爵用大拇指和食指捏着一枚异色的晶石，冲着海因茨怒吼。","id":278},{"type":"text","text":"他的声音嘶哑，愤怒让他难以维持自己的好涵养。","id":279},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您小心，别让它摔在地上。","id":281,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"我给了你七天的时间，为你提供人力物力支持，以供你全力发挥自己在精密切割与宝石改造方面的天分，这就是你的答卷吗？","id":283,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"是、是的，大人。","id":285,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"“是的”？可笑！","id":287,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"海因茨，你是格林登最优秀的宝石鉴定师，难道看不出来，这颗玩意甚至比不上市集上成兜卖的玻璃珠子？","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"这肮脏的金色，稍微靠近一点，就能发现它的内部构造不匀称，光线的折射像是迷了路一样。","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"还有这另一半的黑色，粗糙得像是荒野上的一块卵石，廉价得像是小酒馆不透光的窗帘布。","id":290,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"而这两种颜色的嵌合，如此涣散，如此生硬。","id":291,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"它那梦幻的色泽呢？它那璀璨的星光呢？它那独一无二的色彩交融的美感呢？","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你接下委托，却堂而皇之地给我这么一颗拙劣的假石头，让我将它献给女皇？","id":293,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你想让两位陛下一人一脚踩碎我的脑袋吗？你想让我的高塔被夷为平地吗？","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"海因茨，谁给了你这样的勇气来愚弄我？！","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"charslot","id":297},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"text","text":"“咔嚓”。","id":299},{"type":"text","text":"话音未落，伴随着一声脆响，“双塔之梦”不再完整。那颗异种的双色晶石在萨克森伯爵指间破碎。","id":300},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你该死，海因茨。","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"大人，我的伯爵大人，您真的冤枉我了。请让我证明！","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":305},{"type":"charslot","id":306},{"type":"text","text":"海因茨轻轻旋开法杖中段的阀门。他弯下腰，从地板上捡起一些碎晶填了进去。","id":307},{"type":"text","text":"他稍微向后退了几步，像是在找角度。片刻后，他轻轻打了个响指，法杖顶端应声而亮。","id":308},{"type":"dialog","id":309},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_m","id":310},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"text","text":"粼粼的光闪烁着，深邃的黑色和庄严的金色，像是暮色里的湖泊。","id":313},{"type":"dialog","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"这......","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您当然可以拿它献给女皇。因为它本来就是那颗“双塔之梦”。","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"怎么可能？","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"我刚刚近距离查看了那么久......","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"很简单，伯爵大人。因为“双塔之梦”本身便是一颗很普通的晶石。","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您忘了，是我为它做的鉴定。当时它被放在精美的匣子里，被我法杖的光照耀着。找好角度，控制好光源......","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您看，这不就有了......梦幻的色泽、璀璨的星光。","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"“折光”，我的一点专业技能。","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你？","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您不懂宝石，不该质疑我的专业能力。","id":330,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"......你让我在女皇陛下面前夸下海口，又窃走那颗晶石，故弄玄虚，最后让我亲手毁掉它？","id":332,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你在将整座萨克森伯爵塔逼入绝境！这对你究竟有什么好处？","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"别忘了，是我收容了你，让你来替我的高塔打点宝石生意，是我给了你活路！","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你数一数，凭你那可笑的从业经历......一事无成，还得罪了那么多人，你觉得自己能在格林登混下去吗？","id":335,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"大人，我当然记得您的恩宠。","id":337,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#2$1","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我只是个普通人，那些日子，我几乎快要放弃。","id":339,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"在我将盗来的宝石粉碎成晶末之后，我整晚没有睡着，担心那位偷卖了宝石的书记官会动用市政厅的力量，查到我的头上。","id":341,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"在我出具假的宝石鉴定书，让萨克森子爵出尽洋相断送了仕途时......","id":342,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我无比担心自己的计划太过拙劣，会被您这样善于耍弄阴谋的人物轻易看穿。","id":343,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您果然注意到了我，但好在，您只关心我的使用价值。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#5$1","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"您甚至没有去查证那位倾家荡产的男爵、那位锒铛入狱的书记官具体的身份。","id":347,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"确实......事情已经过去了二十年，您又怎么会记得呢？我们这些小人物，太过无足轻重。","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"你是......什么意思？","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#5$1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我说，我本就为您而来。","id":352,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"从一年半前，我回到格林登，将一颗拙劣的假宝石卖给那位男爵的那一刻起，我的目标就是您，萨克森伯爵。","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"......为什么？","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"哎呀，说了您也记不起来的。","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"对了，女皇之声应该到高塔下了。您向金色的女皇夸下海口，要献出最独一无二的晶石作为女皇庆典的献礼......","id":358,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"该怎么收场呢？","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":360},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"来人！","id":362,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"抓住这个混账！","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"charslot","id":365},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":368},{"type":"text","text":"又一个响指。","id":369},{"type":"text","text":"以法杖为起点，复杂的光线折射发生在空荡荡的露台上。伯爵这才发现，不知何时，露台的各个角落隐藏了许多面镜子。","id":370},{"type":"dialog","id":371},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":372},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":373},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":376},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":377},{"type":"text","text":"光线阻隔了伯爵的视野，再纷纷交汇于海因茨的身体——","id":378},{"type":"text","text":"宝石匠从伯爵的眼前消失了。","id":379},{"type":"text","text":"但最后那一刻，伯爵看见对方的脸上绽开了笑容。","id":380},{"type":"text","text":"一直以来，这个卑躬屈膝的宝石匠都表现得那么谦卑，那么怯懦，那么惹人怜爱......他从未有过如此夸张的笑容。","id":381},{"type":"text","text":"带着嘲弄，带着恨意。","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"祝您好运，伯爵大人。","id":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_492_1#1$1","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨克森伯爵","text":"......","id":385,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_492_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":386},{"type":"charslot","id":387},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":388},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯爵侍从","text":"大、大人，女皇之声已经到了。","id":391},{"type":"dialog","id":392},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":393},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":394},{"type":"charslot","id":395},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":396},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":397},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":398,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":399},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":400},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":401},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":402},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......","id":404,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":405},{"type":"charslot","id":406},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":407},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","duration":"1.5","id":408},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"小朋友，这里可不是乐器工坊，你要是想修理手上的乐器，我可帮不上忙。","id":411,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"戏弄了格林登的伯爵，就打算一走了之？","id":413,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......","id":415,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"海因茨先生，对吧？","id":417,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"米夏埃尔，来自崔林特尔梅。","id":419,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"女皇之声？年纪这么小......","id":421,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"我不是女皇之声，我只是代为传达女皇旨意的密使。","id":423,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"萨克森伯爵的高塔已经被查封，我将押他回崔林特尔梅接受女皇的判决。至于你......","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"嗯哼。","id":426,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"呃，放下你的法杖，别紧张。","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c6/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-10$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"我只是来确认一些事情。","id":430,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"这一年半以来，你经手的宝石生意里，那些遭遇了种种“不幸”的主顾，都有一个共同点。","id":431,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"那个倾家荡产的男爵曾是某个矿场的工头，而那个因无法追回偷卖的宝石而下狱的书记官，曾经负责起草了某起矿难的汇报文书。","id":432,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"......至于萨克森子爵和萨克森伯爵，则是该矿场的所有者。","id":433,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我还以为自己当天就会被抓回高塔的监牢里。隔了整整一天，看来您已经查到了不少事情。","id":435,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"你做这一切，只是为了复仇。对吧？","id":437,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c6/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-10$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"二十多年前，萨克森伯爵在格林登秘密开采源石矿，为巫王打造法阵装置。","id":439,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#7$2","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"可双子女皇政变成功，莱塔尼亚的局势一夕颠覆，两座崭新的高塔在首都拔地而起。","id":441,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"为了方便“投诚”，萨克森伯爵下令将整座源石矿场秘密炸毁，所有的工人都被掩埋......","id":442,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"这件事在他提交给崔林特尔梅的事件说明里，变成了“开采异种晶矿的矿场发生了塌方意外”。","id":444,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......是的，我的父母是那个矿场的工人。","id":446,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我的人生是从那一刻被改变的。","id":447,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"自那天后，我离开格林登，遇见各种人各种事，感染了矿石病，得到这支法杖，只能重新和这些闪亮亮的石头打交道。","id":448,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"好了，尊贵的年轻的密使大人，你还太小，说这些你不懂。","id":450,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"如果你是来确认我的罪行，我想告诉你，我本应设计一场爆炸，把萨克森伯爵也填埋在混杂着碎晶的泥土里。","id":451,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"......","id":453,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"我毁掉了进献给金色女皇的宝石，也没有想过能真的逃脱。直接告知我将受的刑罚吧，密使大人。","id":455,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"海因茨先生，我可以不追究你的责任。对我来说，这起宝石案件，不过是一支插曲。","id":457,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#4$1","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"嗯？","id":459,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/26/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"长期以来，萨克森伯爵一面竭尽所能向女皇献媚，一面暗中资助巫王残党，近年来的数起叛乱事件都与他有关。","id":461,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"我是赫琳玛特的密使，此行便是为了将这只名利的蠹虫带回崔林特尔梅。","id":462,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#7$2","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"至于你毁坏了伊维格娜德为女皇庆典寻求的宝石......那样浮夸的物件，我想赫琳玛特并不感兴趣。","id":464,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"我只是好奇，你已经完成了你的复仇，接下来你如何打算？","id":465,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"......","id":467,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"你现在名气还挺大的，我刚刚在门口的邮箱发现了一封邀请函，顺便给你带进来了。","id":469,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"我查看了你在伯爵塔中的法术装置，你是个优秀的宝石专家，也是一个同样优秀的怪盗。","id":470,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4f/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏埃尔","text":"或许你可以开家宝石鉴定所什么的。我想，在莱塔尼亚，你不缺“生意”。","id":472,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":473},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":474},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":476},{"type":"text","text":"海因茨打开了米夏埃尔留在操作台上的那封邀请函。","id":477},{"type":"text","text":"他认得封面烫金的火漆，那个标志，来自另一座高塔。","id":478},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#1$1","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"“迈尔斯伯爵正携自家矿场出产的罕见晶石——‘天空的珠泪’在莱塔尼亚境内巡展，近期将来到格林登。”","id":480,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"“希望你能在鉴定环节，表现得好一点。”","id":481,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#6$1","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"如果我记得没错，迈尔斯伯爵的矿场去年因为施工防护问题，导致了十多位工人感染，已经被勒令停产了才对......","id":483,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_499_kaitou_1#7$1","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"呵，又一个“萨克森”。","id":485,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海因茨","text":"或许，他的主意并不赖。","id":486,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_499_kaitou_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":487},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":490},{"type":"charslot","id":491},{"type":"image","id":492}],"characters":["海因茨","伯爵侍从","伯爵打手","萨克森伯爵","？？？","米夏埃尔"]}